    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_avlon_416099",
        "quote": "First, I think more Americans need to declare their independence from partisan politics on both sides. The more that Americans declare their independence, the more the parties will have to compete for their votes using reason rather than the hateful appeals.",
        "author": {
            "name": "John Avlon",
            "url": "/quotes/john_avlon_416099"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Politics",
                "url": "/topics/politics"
